      <body>
         <pb n="1" facs="../images/ew_b_001.jpg"/><!-- Here is your first page break. You need to make the image name here match the name of your file -->
         <figure><graphic url="ew_b_001_001.jpg"/></figure>
         <figure><desc>Taken from University of North Florida Special Collections, Eartha M.M. White Collection, Folder B, Item no number.</desc><graphic url="../images/ew_b_001_001.jpg"></graphic></figure>
         <div>
            <head rend="center">
           
            The Afro-American Life Insurance Company<lb/>
               
            </head>
         </div>
         <div>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center">INCORPORATED UNDER THE LAWS OF FLORIDA</hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                 
                  <hi rend="center">PAID UP CAPITAL STOCK $150,000.00</hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center"><name type="person">A.L. LEWIS</name>,<name role="administrator">  PRESIDENT </name>               <name type="person">J.H. LEWIS</name>,<name role="administrator">  VICE PRESIDENT</name></hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center"><name type="person">LOUIS D. ERVIN</name>,<name role="administrator">  CASHIER</name>                 <name type="person">WILLIAM H. LEE</name>,<name role="administrator">  SECRETARY</name></hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center"><name type="place">HOME OFFICE</name> <name type="place" subtype="address"> 101-105 E. UNION STREET<location><geo>30.331966 -81.654918</geo></location></name></hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <name type="place">OFFICE OF PRESIDENT</name> <lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center"><name type="place" subtype="address">P.O. BOX 660</name></hi><lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="center"><name type="place" subtype="city">JACKSONVILLE, FLORIDA</name></hi><lb/>
               </p>
         
         
         </div>
         <div>
            <p>
             <date when="1936-01-18">January 18- 1936</date><lb/>
            </p>  
         </div>
         <div>
            <p>
            <name type="person">Miss Eartha White</name><lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="address">611 West Ashley Street<lb/>
                  Jacksonville, Florida</name><location><geo>30.332490 -81.664152</geo></location><lb/>
            </p>
         </div>
            <div>
              
               <opener>
                  <salute>
                     My dear <name type="person">Miss White</name>:<lb/>
                  </salute>
               </opener>
              
            </div>
         <div>
            <p>
            
            I noticed recently your publication with reference<lb/>
               to<supplied reason="omitted-in-original" cert="high">the</supplied><name type="organization"> History Society for Jacksonville Negroes</name>.<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>
            I have always felt that some one should write a<lb/>
            history of the <name type="person_group">Negroes</name> of our <name type="place">city</name>, as far back<lb/>
            as we can get information, so that in future years<lb/>
            the young generation will know of some of the<lb/>
            accomplishments and hardships. You have my hearty<lb/>
            support and if I can be of any service to you, <lb/>
            call on me.<lb/> 
            </p>
            <p>
               <name type="person">Mayor Aslop</name> called me and stated that he wanted to <lb/>
               appoint you and myself as an <name type="committee">Advisory Committee</name> on<lb/>
               the <name type="legislation">Slum Housing Act</name>, and ask that I talk with <lb/>
           <name type="person">Mr. Bradshaw</name>, who I saw this morning and he<lb/>
               suggested that we talk with <name type="person">Mr. Edwards</name> in <name type="place">Barnett<lb/>
                  Bank building<location><geo>30.328120 -81.659319</geo></location></name> next Monday or Tuesday. Please get<lb/>
            in touch with me for this meeting. 
            </p>
            <p>
            May I wish for you continued good health and success. 
            </p>
         </div>
       
          
            <closer>
               <salute>
                  <hi rend="center">
                     Very truly yours,<lb/>
                  </hi>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person"> <name type="person">A.L. LEWIS</name>,<name role="administrator">  PRESIDENT</name></name>.<lb/>
               </signed>
            </closer>
          
        
         
         
         
           
         <note place="marginLeft">ALL- eaj </note> 
           
